The paper deals with video summarization, which involves computer vision and machine learning techniques to analyze and summarize video content. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses optimization algorithms and metaheuristics, which fall under cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper proposes a novel algorithm for video summarization, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
